@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ogcslj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.46)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.08 - tmp + 0.38)) / ((v1 + 0.44 * v1 + 0.49) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.27)))
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.exp(v2 + 0.05) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.04)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.60)) / (0.02 - wp.sin(v1 + 0.07)))
    v0 = wp.exp(v0)
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.exp(v1 + 0.99) + (v1 + 0.60 * v2 + 0.29)))
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.sin(v2 + 0.41) - 0.62))
    data[tid] = v0
